:::Atma/Psuedo:::

::Atma and Psuedo wake up. For awhile they are confused, but then they 
remember their fight with Clash::
Atma: It seems that our sparks are free. That bot must've died.
Psuedo: Yeah, i guess so...... TECHNOSIS!
Atma: Huh?
Psuedo: Where is she? I have to find her!
Atma: Hey, im as worried as you are, but lets not do anything hasty...
Psuedo: Come on Atma! We have to find out if shes alive!
Atma: Theres another problem for us. When Deemos learns that were alive, 
he'll start hunting us down again.
Psuedo: Well, i say we wander the planet and try to find Technosis. Once shes 
safe with us, we'll think about what faction we'll join.
Atma: I guess thats a good plan.
::The go off in search of Technosis::

--part1_9c.b130102.27a1e301_boundary
